<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="B" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Bepaint" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Bepaint,</orth> do dye: <cit><quote>whose frothy mouth, --ed all with red,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ven 901" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 901</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>else would a maiden blush b. my cheek,</quote> <bibl n="shak. rom 2.2.86" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. II, 2, 86</bibl></cit>.
